data.description: PRICED WELL BELOW MARKET VALUE FOR QUICK SALE!!!  Hill top home with amazing views! Lots of thought went into placing this 1600 sq ft manufactured home in the best possible spot on 10.03 acres to take advantage of the beautiful views of the surrounding mountains and distant lights. Inside you will find two generous sized bedrooms, a spacious family room with fireplace and another huge living / family gathering room – this inviting room is on the east wing, is semi-private, has a wood burning stove with built-in wooden cabinetry wrapped around one end and has the potential to be setup as a 3 rd bedroom / sleeping quarters (it was used as an office + dining + sitting room prior – yes all in one room!). Warm, welll maintained wood paneling throughout. The central wrap-around kitchen is the main focus of this popular floor plan. Outside is a generous, multi-tiered deck with a built-in BBQ and outdoor wet bar area with sink and countertop. Enjoy those balmy summer evenings with a cool drink out on the patio while the sun sets on the distant mountains. The master bathroom is separate and has a large tub for soaking and its own deck. There is a dedicated laundry room with sink and storage. Outside the back door is a roomy workshop with lots of storage and room for your hobbies. This lot is part of parcel map #9684 with dedicated roads and easements. The double carport offers protection for your vehicles with convenient access to the back entry. Use your imagination to upgrade this home to your liking. Choose your flooring! A little facelift and TLC is all she needs. RV hook-ups just outside. Main well pumps 45 gallons per minute according to the well report with fantastic tasting water. Enough for a very large garden or small farm. There is also a 2 nd well that is currently capped. EZ freeway access and lots of space to spread your wings. All appliances convey with the property with no warranty.
